<section id="Leadership Council September 2024 Representative Selections" class="white">
  <div class="w-100 mw-none ph3 mw8-m mw8-l center f3">
    <header>
      <h2>Leadership Council September 2024 Representative Selections</h2>
      <div class="highlight mt2 mb3"></div>
    </header>

    <div class="publish-date-author">Sept. 27, 2024 &middot; Eric Huss
     on behalf of <a href="https://www.rust-lang.org/governance/teams/leadership-council">Leadership Council</a> 
    </div>

    <div class="post">
      <p>The September 2024 selections for <a href="https://www.rust-lang.org/governance/teams/leadership-council">Leadership Council</a> representatives have been finalized. The Lang Team has chosen <a href="https://github.com/traviscross">TC</a> as their new representative, and the Moderation Team has chosen <a href="https://github.com/oli-obk">Oliver Scherer</a>. Oli is currently on leave, so the current representative, <a href="https://github.com/technetos">Josh Gould</a>, will substitute until he returns. Thank you to the outgoing representatives <a href="https://github.com/jackh726">Jack Huey</a> and <a href="https://github.com/technetos">Josh Gould</a> for your amazing support on the Council.</p>
<p>The representatives chosen this round are:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.rust-lang.org/governance/teams/infra">Infra</a> — <a href="https://github.com/Mark-Simulacrum">Mark Rousskov</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.rust-lang.org/governance/teams/lang">Lang</a> — <a href="https://github.com/traviscross">TC</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.rust-lang.org/governance/teams/library">Libs</a> — <a href="https://github.com/m-ou-se">Mara Bos</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.rust-lang.org/governance/teams/moderation">Mods</a> — <a href="https://github.com/oli-obk">Oliver Scherer</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Thanks to everyone who participated in the process! The next representative selections will be in March 2025 for the other half of the Council.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
